
    A YOUNG girl and a man were killed in a crash just
outside Rustenburg in the North West on Christmas morning."Shortly before 8am, paramedics from ER24, fire
services and other EMS personnel arrived on the scene where they found… two
vehicles mangled together,” ER24 spokesman Werner Vermaak said.The girl, believed to be between 5 and 7 years old, and
the man were already dead when they were found in one of the cars. Their
